title: Stade El-Hadj-Mamadou-Coulibaly
text: Stade Municipal is a multi-use <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="Odienne">Odienne</a>, <a href="C%C3%B4te%20d%27Ivoire">Côte d'Ivoire</a>. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches. It serves as a home ground of <a href="Denguel%C3%A9%20Sports%20d%27Odienn%C3%A9">Denguelé Sports d'Odienné</a>. The stadium holds 3,000 people.
